transcript.text: Accepting partial payment is made easy with on Print Shop.
After enabling this feature, simply set up your payment terms.
For example, you can set 20% at order placement, 30% after 10 days, and the remaining 50% after 20 days of order placement.
You can assign any of these payment terms to individual customers or stores now.
During checkout, customers can then select the partial payment method and place the order.
For subsequent installments, admins can raise further payment requests.
